data.description: Move-in ready home within a short walking distance from the elementary school! This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home features approximately 1,410 sqft, a formal living room, family room open to the kitchen with granite countertops, a breakfast area, and a covered patio with a large backyard big enough to fit a pool to enjoy the outdoors. Plus, the A/C unit has been recently replaced with an all new system! Hurry and call your favorite Realtor today to schedule a showing!
